WEBVTT

00:11.100 --> 00:12.634
We have brought upon us

00:12.636 --> 00:17.405
our own destruction, my beloved.

00:17.407 --> 00:20.341
It was without form and void.

00:20.343 --> 00:24.112
Unto the heavens and
they had no light.

00:24.114 --> 00:28.583
I looked and behold,
there was no man.

00:28.585 --> 00:32.787
I looked and behold, the
fruitful land was a desert.

00:32.789 --> 00:37.158
And its cities were laid
in ruins before the lord.

00:37.160 --> 00:40.495
Before his fierce anger
for thus, said the lord,

00:40.497 --> 00:43.665
"the whole land
shall be desolation."

00:45.100 --> 00:50.605
Jeremiah, chapter 4:23-27.

00:50.607 --> 00:53.675
It is said by the unwise,

00:53.677 --> 00:57.578
by the unbelievers
that death comes to us

00:57.580 --> 01:00.982
in the visage of a reaper

01:00.984 --> 01:04.319
harvesting his crops
with a great scythe.

01:04.321 --> 01:07.789
But we've been
taught differently.

01:07.791 --> 01:10.491
For the trumpet will sound

01:10.493 --> 01:13.928
and the dead will be
raised imperishable.

01:13.930 --> 01:18.533
And this mortal body
must put on immortality.

01:18.535 --> 01:19.667
Behold.

01:19.669 --> 01:20.735
Hey there.

01:21.804 --> 01:26.741
Just this stuff and...

01:26.743 --> 01:29.811
Let's make it...

01:29.813 --> 01:32.680
$12.92 in gas.

01:32.682 --> 01:37.418
<i>By an epidemic,
an epidemic of sin.</i>

01:37.420 --> 01:42.590
<i>We have brought upon us our
own destruction, my beloved.</i>

01:42.592 --> 01:46.627
<i>I am the resurrection
and the life,</i>

01:46.629 --> 01:49.664
<i>whoever believes in me</i>

01:49.666 --> 01:51.632
<i>though he die yet</i>

01:51.634 --> 01:54.302
<i>shall he live.</i>

01:54.304 --> 01:56.637
I love him.

01:56.639 --> 02:00.108
How can you love
somebody you've never met?

02:01.744 --> 02:03.811
Don't over-pump.

02:03.813 --> 02:05.780
You have a nice day too.

02:05.782 --> 02:09.817
And honey, be careful,
there are crazies out there.

