Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:33.308 --> 02:34.308
Hey!

02:35.244 --> 02:36.344
Hey!

02:36.346 --> 02:37.845
Hey you, please!

02:38.614 --> 02:39.680
Please you have to help me!

02:39.682 --> 02:41.349
You have to help me,
no, no, no, come on.

02:41.351 --> 02:42.884
Okay, okay, okay.

02:50.026 --> 02:51.626
Can you please help him?

02:51.628 --> 02:53.628
He's not contagious is he?

02:53.630 --> 02:55.830
Hey hey hey hey hey hey.

02:55.832 --> 02:58.266
Okay wait, your name
is Richard Hanna.

02:58.268 --> 03:02.503
We've been married 10 years,
come on, remember?

03:02.505 --> 03:04.872
Stay with me, stay with me.

03:05.574 --> 03:07.275
What's your name, sweetie?

03:07.277 --> 03:10.611
Um, Dee, I'm Dee.

03:10.613 --> 03:12.613
He's dying, isn't he?

03:12.615 --> 03:14.649
I don't know, Dee,
maybe we should take him

03:14.651 --> 03:15.917
to the hospital.

03:15.919 --> 03:20.188
No, emergency room was
overflowing, people everywhere.

03:20.190 --> 03:21.756
He wanted to try somewhere else

03:21.758 --> 03:25.126
and um, I shouldn't
have listened to him.

03:25.128 --> 03:27.829
I think running made it worse.

03:28.964 --> 03:31.365
Mommy, what's a Sisyphus?

03:34.803 --> 03:37.105
Dee, let me call
an ambulance, okay?

03:37.107 --> 03:40.575
I'm sorry, I don't
know what else to do.

04:06.135 --> 04:09.971
That was a nice thing
you did for that lady.

04:09.973 --> 04:12.039
Your detritus.

04:54.349 --> 04:55.149
Hi.

04:55.151 --> 04:56.484
Hey Kirbs.

04:56.486 --> 04:57.685
What's up?

04:57.687 --> 04:59.487
Just checkin' in with you.

04:59.489 --> 05:02.456
Hey did you know the family from <i> the
hills have eyes</i> opened a gas station?

05:02.458 --> 05:03.658
On your way?

05:03.660 --> 05:05.293
You betcha.

05:05.295 --> 05:06.861
Maybe sometime
you'll let me come

05:06.863 --> 05:08.529
to your place.

05:08.531 --> 05:10.598
Let's uh, not have
this conversation

05:10.600 --> 05:11.799
for the millionth time.

05:11.801 --> 05:13.801
I could meet your friends.

05:13.803 --> 05:15.169
They're all jerks.

05:15.171 --> 05:17.438
Could cook you my pizza rolls.

05:17.440 --> 05:19.674
Real pizza, my treat.

05:19.676 --> 05:22.009
You don't sleep well in my bed.

05:22.011 --> 05:25.112
I'm not going there to sleep.

05:25.114 --> 05:27.114
You just winked
to the phone, didn't you?

05:27.116 --> 05:28.783
Maybe.

05:28.785 --> 05:32.186
Fine, you just got me wondering

05:32.188 --> 05:33.788
if you've got heads
in your freezer.

05:33.790 --> 05:34.790
Uh huh.

05:39.995 --> 05:42.196
Wait, I'm coming
up on another one.

05:43.466 --> 05:45.199
There's an outback.

05:45.201 --> 05:47.201
A rendezvous
just rolled past my place.

05:47.203 --> 05:49.270
Oh my god.

05:49.272 --> 05:51.739
Oh wait, here's another one.

05:52.574 --> 05:55.810
It's a breeze.

05:57.145 --> 05:58.746
Hello?

05:58.748 --> 05:59.748
Hello?

06:00.616 --> 06:01.716
Damn it.

06:14.696 --> 06:15.830
Shit.

06:27.777 --> 06:29.010
God damn-it.

06:52.868 --> 06:55.803
License and registration.

06:55.805 --> 06:57.605
No bullshit please.

07:03.245 --> 07:06.247
Having ourselves a
little road trip are we?

07:06.249 --> 07:10.518
Skills like that you'll
make detective in no time.

07:13.255 --> 07:16.090
Hey, I have the
same phone as you.

07:33.408 --> 07:34.408
Miss Lane.

07:34.410 --> 07:36.677
Don't sneak up on me like that!

07:36.679 --> 07:39.680
Do you know why I
pulled you over today?

07:39.682 --> 07:42.583
To protect everybody
else on the road?

07:42.585 --> 07:45.019
Everyone's a comedian, huh?

07:45.021 --> 07:46.687
I wrote you up for speeding

07:46.689 --> 07:47.822
and dangerous operation.

07:47.824 --> 07:49.590
That's a $500 fine.

07:49.592 --> 07:51.859
But there's nobody else
to endanger, come on!

07:51.861 --> 07:53.861
Listen, I'm too tired
to argue with you,

07:53.863 --> 07:55.730
so um, how 'bout this?

07:57.666 --> 07:59.934
I will agree to tear
up your citation

07:59.936 --> 08:03.337
if you agree to take
a nap for 60 minutes

08:03.339 --> 08:06.107
and decide to drive slow
for the rest of your trip.

08:06.109 --> 08:07.108
Really?

08:07.110 --> 08:10.611
60 minutes, I want your word.

08:10.613 --> 08:11.613
Sold.

08:15.650 --> 08:18.786
I'll radio in that I let
you off with a warning.

08:18.788 --> 08:20.821
You drive safely now.

09:04.666 --> 09:08.002
Please, please,
please, please, please.

09:18.580 --> 09:20.114
Thank you for calling Northstar,

09:20.116 --> 09:22.316
this is Max, am I
speaking to Kirby Lane?

09:22.318 --> 09:22.316
Yes.

09:22.318 --> 09:24.685
How can I help
you tonight, miss Lane?

09:24.687 --> 09:26.987
This piece of shit car won't go.

09:26.989 --> 09:30.658
Okay, miss Lane,
I understand this is a

09:30.660 --> 09:32.026
taxing situation.

09:32.028 --> 09:35.129
I go out and I get all this
turbo this, road side that,

09:35.131 --> 09:38.098
and then when I need the car,
it craps on itself and dies.

09:38.100 --> 09:40.801
Now miss Lane,
I'm sure it's not dead.

09:40.803 --> 09:43.971
It has big Xs where the
headlights used to be.

09:43.973 --> 09:47.408
Okay, well, let's
see what we have here.

09:47.410 --> 09:50.277
Okay, have you been doing
routine maintenance?

09:50.279 --> 09:52.913
Tire pressure, changing the oil?

09:55.183 --> 09:56.317
Yes?

09:56.319 --> 09:58.752
Uh huh, I see.

09:58.754 --> 10:01.789
Are you hurt or in any danger?

10:01.791 --> 10:04.792
I think I heard some
wolverines earlier.

10:04.794 --> 10:07.027
Well, according
to our records, miss Lane,

10:07.029 --> 10:10.431
that SUV of yours is the
next best thing to a tank.

10:10.433 --> 10:11.699
You should be fine.

10:11.701 --> 10:16.871
But uh, looks like your
transmission's fried.

10:16.873 --> 10:18.606
I'm stuck in neutral.

10:18.608 --> 10:20.608
All right, I'll put
a call in for a tow truck,

10:20.610 --> 10:24.512
but based on your location,
it's gonna be a few hours.

10:24.514 --> 10:25.613
Hours?

10:25.615 --> 10:27.681
Maybe I should just walk.

10:27.683 --> 10:29.783
Don't be a hero, miss Lane.

10:29.785 --> 10:33.587
Just sit tight, okay,
help is on the way.

10:33.589 --> 10:34.855
Thanks tons.

10:34.857 --> 10:36.123
I'll check in
on you later, miss Lane.

10:36.125 --> 10:37.958
Thank you for using Northstar.

10:37.960 --> 10:39.026
Thank you,

10:40.595 --> 10:41.829
Mr. personality.

10:50.639 --> 10:52.206
Call voice mail.

10:52.208 --> 10:54.475
Calling voice mail.

11:04.619 --> 11:07.021
You have no messages.

11:18.867 --> 11:21.936
Jesus!

11:25.106 --> 11:26.106
Dammit.

11:32.514 --> 11:33.514
Shit!

11:42.090 --> 11:43.624
Where the fuck are you?

11:43.626 --> 11:46.860
Car broke down and the
stupid tow truck is taking

11:46.862 --> 11:48.796
the scenic route.

11:48.798 --> 11:50.764
You wanna go to video?

11:50.766 --> 11:52.666
You bet I do.

11:56.338 --> 11:58.639
You look a little wobbly.

11:58.641 --> 12:03.043
Well I am feeling
a little frisky.

12:04.312 --> 12:06.347
I've had a long day, sweetie,

12:06.349 --> 12:09.016
and my phone's about to die,
so...

12:10.652 --> 12:14.588
Sounds like somebody
needs to unwind a bit.

12:14.590 --> 12:17.625
I can help you
with that you know.

12:17.627 --> 12:22.196
I specialize in
getting you to unwind.

12:24.466 --> 12:25.599
Besides, what else
are you gonna do

12:25.601 --> 12:28.035
'til the tow truck gets there?

13:07.642 --> 13:10.477
I cannot wait to be with you.

13:46.781 --> 13:48.282
Thank you for calling north...

13:48.284 --> 13:50.117
where the fuck is my tow truck?

13:50.119 --> 13:51.819
I've been waiting for hours.

13:51.821 --> 13:53.987
Miss Lane?

13:53.989 --> 13:57.424
Great, world champion
of customer service.

13:57.426 --> 13:58.992
Lemme talk to someone else.

13:58.994 --> 14:00.661
I'm the only one here.

14:00.663 --> 14:01.962
Yeah, you mean you're
the only one there willing

14:01.964 --> 14:03.197
to talk to me.

14:03.199 --> 14:05.999
No, I mean
I'm the only one here.

14:06.001 --> 14:08.602
Where's that damn tow, Max?

14:12.609 --> 14:13.508
Well?

14:13.509 --> 14:15.843
I don't know
what's going on, miss Lane,

14:15.845 --> 14:18.145
I put the order in last
night for a dispatcher and,

14:18.147 --> 14:19.513
look, I just sent another one.

14:19.515 --> 14:20.814
But I'm getting no response.

14:20.816 --> 14:22.416
Well, what am I supposed to do,

14:22.418 --> 14:24.585
hitch a ride on a camel?

14:24.587 --> 14:27.855
Can you flag down another car?

14:32.026 --> 14:35.295
I think I took the exit
to the "twilight zone."

14:35.297 --> 14:38.532
Miss Lane,
I've got some bad news.

14:38.534 --> 14:39.534
For a change?

14:41.336 --> 14:43.804
I'm gonna have to
call you back in a second.

14:43.806 --> 14:44.605
Sit tight, okay?

14:44.607 --> 14:45.706
Fine.

14:59.654 --> 15:02.689
I have no idea what I'm doing.

15:02.691 --> 15:03.824
Hello?

15:09.664 --> 15:11.932
Jesus, mister, are you sick?

15:16.137 --> 15:17.638
Whoa man, don't come any closer!

15:17.640 --> 15:21.909
Back off or else I'm gonna
brain you with this thing.

15:23.411 --> 15:25.913
Jesus Christ!

15:27.115 --> 15:28.448
I'm sorry!

15:28.450 --> 15:31.518
Um, oh Jesus are you dead?

15:32.654 --> 15:35.455
Listen, I'm sorry,
you wouldn't listen to me

15:35.457 --> 15:37.090
and I...
God, I'm so sorry.

15:41.430 --> 15:42.763
Jesus! Fuck!

15:47.335 --> 15:50.871
Max, a tow truck would be
past wonderful right now.

15:50.873 --> 15:52.139
Why, what's happened?

15:52.141 --> 15:54.441
There's a man,
there's a crazy man.

15:54.443 --> 15:57.444
Okay Kirby, stay
calm, keep the doors locked

15:57.446 --> 15:58.245
and the windows up, okay?

15:58.247 --> 16:00.247
Christ, there's another one!

16:00.249 --> 16:02.583
Jesus, they're coming
out of everywhere.

16:02.585 --> 16:04.451
Look, I know this is
gonna sound stupid right now,

16:04.453 --> 16:05.686
but you need to stay calm.

16:05.688 --> 16:06.987
Calm? Max...

16:06.989 --> 16:08.522
I just buried my
wrench through the forehead

16:08.524 --> 16:10.791
of this man, and he's
still banging on my window.

16:10.793 --> 16:12.092
I know.

16:12.094 --> 16:13.794
You know?
How do you know?

16:13.796 --> 16:15.662
Well, we've been getting
reports like this all day.

16:15.664 --> 16:17.164
Something sort of
crazy is happening.

16:17.166 --> 16:18.599
You can say that again.

16:18.601 --> 16:20.000
Some kind of outbreak.

16:20.002 --> 16:22.803
It's making people crazy.

16:22.805 --> 16:23.804
Just stay in the car,
Kirby, all right?

16:23.806 --> 16:25.606
Help is on the way.

16:57.038 --> 16:58.605
Kirby?

16:58.607 --> 16:59.539
What?

16:59.541 --> 17:01.508
What happened?

17:01.510 --> 17:05.579
I just got rescued by
the cast of <i> deliverance.</i>

17:16.758 --> 17:18.492
One of them's coming
this way, I gotta go.

17:18.493 --> 17:20.160
Wait, Kirby.

17:22.997 --> 17:23.997
You bit?

17:25.666 --> 17:26.666
What?

17:27.769 --> 17:29.870
You look clean enough.

17:29.872 --> 17:32.372
What are you doing out here?

17:33.775 --> 17:36.109
Waiting for my tow truck.

17:37.011 --> 17:38.078
Tow truck?

17:39.614 --> 17:40.881
Call me the captain
of the obvious,

17:40.883 --> 17:43.350
but I don't think it's coming.

17:46.287 --> 17:49.222
Fucking head exploded man.

17:52.694 --> 17:56.129
Dirty, dirty
fucking shit out there.

17:56.131 --> 17:58.999
So how many kills you get today?

18:00.668 --> 18:01.902
Lost count.

18:04.939 --> 18:06.173
Whatever it was,
it was a damn sight

18:06.175 --> 18:09.076
more than miss pinky over here.

18:09.078 --> 18:10.078
Bullshit.

18:11.579 --> 18:12.546
Bullshit?

18:12.548 --> 18:14.648
I'm not not talking about
winging some fuckers,

18:14.650 --> 18:17.184
I'm talking about kill shots.

18:19.520 --> 18:21.421
Kill shots, huh?

18:21.423 --> 18:24.858
Why don't you go see
if our girl's hungry?

18:26.694 --> 18:28.495
Don't mind if I do.

18:39.507 --> 18:40.507
Hungry?

18:48.316 --> 18:51.351
Look who's decided
to join the party.

18:51.353 --> 18:54.154
Park your little butt fireside.

18:55.423 --> 18:57.190
What's on the menu?

18:58.659 --> 18:59.659
Barbecue.

19:07.502 --> 19:09.469
It's something.

19:09.471 --> 19:10.670
Try it out, baby.

19:17.745 --> 19:19.413
It's kinda flat.

19:24.420 --> 19:27.487
Oh, she's a pretty one,
isn't she?

19:38.200 --> 19:39.200
That's it.

19:43.004 --> 19:44.171
Then nothing.

20:03.858 --> 20:05.125
That's disgusting.

20:05.127 --> 20:07.527
Hey, don't knock
it till you've tried.

20:07.529 --> 20:09.162
You actually eat them?

20:09.164 --> 20:13.433
Well, hell, everything's
got its uses, even them.

20:14.502 --> 20:16.036
You sure you don't want none?

20:16.038 --> 20:18.872
Thanks, I had ears for lunch.

20:24.645 --> 20:26.613
Intestinal lining?

20:26.615 --> 20:28.748
It's chicken noodle soup.

20:34.989 --> 20:37.457
Aren't you afraid
that you're gonna like...

20:37.459 --> 20:38.258
what?

20:38.260 --> 20:39.260
Turn?

20:42.497 --> 20:45.632
Been watching too much TV, girl.

20:45.634 --> 20:49.636
Only way you can turn
is by getting bit.

20:49.638 --> 20:52.672
And that's why we all got
a pact with each other.

20:52.674 --> 20:54.474
What kinda pact?

20:54.476 --> 20:55.675
Death pact.

20:57.745 --> 21:02.616
Any one of us gets bit, falls
to the others do the job

21:02.618 --> 21:05.685
before we become like them.

21:05.687 --> 21:09.456
Mm, aw, that's the stuff.

21:09.458 --> 21:11.224
I'll take your word for it.

21:14.762 --> 21:16.496
So where'd they come from?

21:16.498 --> 21:20.634
Ya know, like why, why
are they like that?

21:20.636 --> 21:21.735
I dunno.

21:22.970 --> 21:27.007
Just woke up one day and the
whole world went to hell.

21:31.646 --> 21:33.213
Where you headed?

21:34.415 --> 21:35.916
City.

21:38.587 --> 21:40.020
Talk about hell.

21:41.122 --> 21:42.122
Why?

21:43.124 --> 21:46.092
Shit, that whole place is
crawling with creepers.

21:46.094 --> 21:48.161
There's gotta be
some help though.

21:48.163 --> 21:49.262
What about the government?

21:52.333 --> 21:53.900
Shit, government.

21:54.769 --> 21:56.670
You trust them?

21:56.672 --> 21:58.672
Gotta trust something?

21:58.674 --> 22:00.273
How the hell do you
know they're not the ones

22:00.275 --> 22:02.342
that caused this
in the first place?

22:02.344 --> 22:04.744
I'd say it was
those damn liberals.

22:04.746 --> 22:07.347
You think everything
was liberals.

22:07.349 --> 22:09.583
Yeah, that's 'cause
almost everything is.

22:09.585 --> 22:12.686
With their doctors and
their scientists trying

22:12.688 --> 22:16.590
to play god, well,
you reap what you sow.

22:16.592 --> 22:18.358
Here we go.

22:18.360 --> 22:20.594
Be not deceived,
god is not mocked,

22:20.596 --> 22:23.330
for whatsoever a man
reapeth he shall also sow.

22:23.332 --> 22:24.798
Galatians 6:7.

22:24.800 --> 22:25.800
Okay.

22:26.801 --> 22:28.568
That's all this is.

22:30.104 --> 22:33.640
God's little way of reminding
us he's still in charge.

22:33.642 --> 22:35.408
Yeah, well, I don't
think god has anything

22:35.410 --> 22:36.776
to do with this.

22:36.778 --> 22:38.511
No?

22:38.513 --> 22:40.180
Probably a democrat too.

22:40.182 --> 22:43.783
I'm not discussing
that with you, okay.

22:43.785 --> 22:46.119
I knew it, goddamned
liberal here in our midst.

22:46.121 --> 22:49.789
All right, enough
already, ravage.

22:49.791 --> 22:52.092
Blondie here's our guest.

22:52.094 --> 22:54.761
I don't know, never
did much trust a woman

22:54.763 --> 22:57.597
who's afraid to
eat a little meat.

23:10.946 --> 23:12.579
He ain't coming.

23:12.581 --> 23:13.680
What?

23:13.682 --> 23:15.448
You still waiting
on that tow truck,

23:15.450 --> 23:19.719
but uh, I think he's got
problems plenty of his own.

23:21.789 --> 23:23.590
Drink?

23:23.592 --> 23:24.658
No thanks.

23:26.127 --> 23:27.394
More for me.

23:32.767 --> 23:33.867
So,

23:35.870 --> 23:38.004
you know, we should just
go ahead and get started.

23:38.006 --> 23:39.673
Get started?

23:39.675 --> 23:41.941
God, I don't think so, man.

23:41.943 --> 23:44.644
Oh, that's no way to be.

23:44.646 --> 23:46.980
After all, I did save your life.

23:46.982 --> 23:48.548
I'm outta here.

23:51.119 --> 23:52.585
Fucking bitch.

23:54.322 --> 23:56.256
I warned you.

23:56.258 --> 23:58.758
Got me a feisty one here.

23:58.760 --> 24:00.860
Hey, game on, smokes?

24:03.764 --> 24:04.831
